                  <textLang mainLang="la">Latin</textLang>
                  <msItem>
                     <p> Memorandum, in which <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename>, archbishop of <placeName type="diocese" role="archbishop" key="place_104006">Canterbury</placeName>
                        </persName>, 
                  certifies that the payment of an annual pension of 60s. from the church of <placeName key="place_106198">Wodeham Ferrers</placeName>, 
                  for two parts of the tithes of the whole of the lordship of <placeName key="place_106198">Wodeham</placeName>, to the abbot and
                  <orgName key="org_105001">convent of Bec Herlewin</orgName>, shall be made by 
                  <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> de <surname>Ferrers</surname>, rector</persName> of the said church, 
                  during his life. 
                  Dated at Eeynes the Ides of June, <origDate when="1303">1303</origDate>. 
                  </p>
                  </msItem>
